{"tid":1871370,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"呢間野食人血饅頭，比人發現後就del post","createTime":"2020-02-09T11:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T09:47:08.000Z","uid":153835,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"622525cd7411171f2afd4adc8f7cad67ba9fef98","tid":1871370,"uid":153835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T11:44:38.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我之前上網見到佢賣搓手液，發現要做會員先買到，登記會員果陣有問題，然後打電話上去問佢，點知無啦啦比佢屌（話唔會幫我，係咁先）<br />\n<br />\n結果有fd買完仲未收到貨，上fb後發現佢想r likes，比人屌完之後就del post，罪證如下：<br />\n<br />\n1.r 10000like先捐60幾支<br />\n開post r likes，話10000個like就捐價值$10000貨出去（本身得1000-2000likes，而且冇講捐去邊），計番佢價錢$149一支，都係捐得67支（佢喺fb自爆第二批貨有5000支，依家仲話有第四批，照計條數由第一批去到第三批可能有4000支啦），照咁計法，4批都賺3球（唔知佢成本幾多啦）<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ym6m4NF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fym6m4NF.jpg&h=a0b63b9b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jqGaX7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjqGaX7G.jpg&h=7a5cf3bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 扮黃<br />\n本身個page只係賣狗仔野，上年6月到依家都冇表過態，突然賣搓手液就講到香港人要小心etc，仲要見到好多同路人叫佢加油之類，真係好撚嘔心<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CD214NP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCD214NP.jpg&h=26caa899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 態度差<br />\nComment覆人串77，打電話上去問野仲要比佢屌同cut線，其實我當初想買都係因為需要，果陣周圍都仲未有貨，而且睇個價錢都算ok。但依家睇返佢當時講電話同埋facebook講野既態度，似係想同人講：依家全世界都搵我買，洗撚理你感受，反正大把人買<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r70nPeD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr70nPeD.jpg&h=30092dc9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kpo1kmi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKpo1kmi.jpg&h=19664101&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.加價<br />\n本身賣$139，突然話成本增加要賣$149 （極可能因為頭兩批好快比人搶完，所以想cap多d水而加價）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/02/09/193524_61b37f9b0cd73ee30b03948020e5c533.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F02%2F09%2F193524_61b37f9b0cd73ee30b03948020e5c533.jpeg&h=516908f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.呃正評<br />\n叫d客寫好評，睇返原來有舊評論屌過佢（疑似舊員工），話佢態度差同唔出糧。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GhFi61y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGhFi61y.jpg&h=3e45f622&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHi rick,聽我電話果陣唔係好串既咩？覆人既時候唔係好串既咩？做咩del post呀？"},{"pid":"066be84bf23051343844a549153eb45618953bad","tid":1871370,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T11:45:04.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻你地討論sorrysorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\np牌開post... 借個位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">上個月粉嶺PTU 16槍 懷疑槍決手足</span><br />\n真相未明 無後續？<br />\n叫曬救命 點解要開槍？？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1871201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1871201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"48a6e7a1d4ce1eba60c4b91a1d8f6456fb0b17ac","tid":1871370,"uid":5540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T11:48:16.000Z","msg":"之前上fb 見到仲以為好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3bd0ad77277e728945e984419fdedba514bbed","tid":1871370,"uid":153835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48a6e7a1d4ce1eba60c4b91a1d8f6456fb0b17ac","tid":1871370,"uid":5540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T11:48:16.000Z","msg":"之前上fb 見到仲以為好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T11:49:26.000Z","msg":"結果我冇訂，但有fd訂左仲未到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc28dbc7726be14acf42a37b1551347009c85de3","tid":1871370,"uid":42814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T11:56: