ass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae86050f57015be053dbf87e8b25327741c1e94","tid":1871370,"uid":193898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T13:00:00.000Z","msg":"有冇多啲料爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"953e305d02002c92be08454d078b010ad6ae604a","tid":1871370,"uid":348745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"622525cd7411171f2afd4adc8f7cad67ba9fef98","tid":1871370,"uid":153835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T11:44:38.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我之前上網見到佢賣搓手液，發現要做會員先買到，登記會員果陣有問題，然後打電話上去問佢，點知無啦啦比佢屌（話唔會幫我，係咁先）<br />\n<br />\n結果有fd買完仲未收到貨，上fb後發現佢想r likes，比人屌完之後就del post，罪證如下：<br />\n<br />\n1.r 10000like先捐60幾支<br />\n開post r likes，話10000個like就捐價值$10000貨出去（本身得1000-2000likes，而且冇講捐去邊），計番佢價錢$149一支，都係捐得67支（佢喺fb自爆第二批貨有5000支，依家仲話有第四批，照計條數由第一批去到第三批可能有4000支啦），照咁計法，4批都賺3球（唔知佢成本幾多啦）<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ym6m4NF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fym6m4NF.jpg&h=a0b63b9b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jqGaX7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjqGaX7G.jpg&h=7a5cf3bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 扮黃<br />\n本身個page只係賣狗仔野，上年6月到依家都冇表過態，突然賣搓手液就講到香港人要小心etc，仲要見到好多同路人叫佢加油之類，真係好撚嘔心<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CD214NP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCD214NP.jpg&h=26caa899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 態度差<br />\nComment覆人串77，打電話上去問野仲要比佢屌同cut線，其實我當初想買都係因為需要，果陣周圍都仲未有貨，而且睇個價錢都算ok。但依家睇返佢當時講電話同埋facebook講野既態度，似係想同人講：依家全世界都搵我買，洗撚理你感受，反正大把人買<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r70nPeD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr70nPeD.jpg&h=30092dc9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kpo1kmi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKpo1kmi.jpg&h=19664101&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.加價<br />\n本身賣$139，突然話成本增加要賣$149 （極可能因為頭兩批好快比人搶完，所以想cap多d水而加價）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/02/09/193524_61b37f9b0cd73ee30b03948020e5c533.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F02%2F09%2F193524_61b37f9b0cd73ee30b03948020e5c533.jpeg&h=516908f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.呃正評<br />\n叫d客寫好評，睇返原來有舊評論屌過佢（疑似舊員工），話佢態度差同唔出糧。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GhFi61y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGhFi61y.jpg&h=3e45f622&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHi rick,聽我電話果陣唔係好串既咩？覆人既時候唔係好串既咩？做咩del post呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T13:00:10.000Z","msg":"呢條友幾好笑 個page先得2000個like 要一晚多5倍 真係有錢派都做唔到啦 咁先肯捐幾十支 一睇就知係仆街啦<br />\n真係唔係錢嘅問題 係人格問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw今晚如果我今晚六合彩中多過6個字 我會捐價值$10000的口罩去慈善機構（曲）"},{"pid":"069725413b430c8d279938b208043c0ec33df6bb","tid":1871370,"uid":153835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ae86050f57015be053dbf87e8b25327741c1e94","tid":1871370,"uid":193898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T13:00:00.000Z","msg":"有冇多啲料爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T13:01:51.000Z","msg":"睇下有冇識佢既人爆下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7418045a8917d6a3fd8f126caa668b6f478e9ae","tid":1871370,"uid":153835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"069725413b430c8d279938b208043c0ec33df6bb","tid":1871370,"uid":153835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ae86050f57015be053dbf87e8b25327741c1e94","tid":1871370,"uid":193898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T13:00:00.000Z","msg":"有冇多啲料爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T13:01:51.000Z","msg":"睇下有冇識佢既人爆下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T13:07:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BGaOLio.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=h